root: ^Having finally gotten my own house in the countryside, like I had been dreaming of, Rebecca wanted to talk about moving in together, again.
^We had been an official couple for two years at this point and she felt ready to take the next step in our relationship.
^But with the grief and shock of my grandfather’s passing still lingering close, I made it into a fight.
^I said things I regret, things I didn’t mean or shouldn’t have said at all and I fled
